# HTML Structure Rules

## Required Meta Tags
- UTF-8 character set
- Viewport meta tag for responsive design
- Description meta tag for SEO
- Google Fonts import (Poppins and Open Sans)

## Main Sections
1. Header
   - Logo
   - Navigation menu
   - Mobile menu button

2. Hero Section
   - Background image
   - Main heading
   - Subheading
   - Call-to-action button

3. Featured Dishes
   - Section heading
   - Grid of featured items
   - Each item should have image and description

4. Menu Section
   - Section heading
   - Menu categories
   - Menu items with prices

5. Why Choose Us
   - Section heading
   - Grid of features
   - Icons and descriptions

6. Footer
   - Contact information
   - Social media links
   - Copyright notice

## Required Classes
- Use BEM naming convention
- Container classes for layout
- Section-specific classes
- Utility classes for common elements

## Semantic Elements
- Use appropriate HTML5 semantic elements
- Maintain proper heading hierarchy
- Use descriptive alt text for images
- Include ARIA labels where needed

## Accessibility Requirements
- Proper heading structure
- Alt text for images
- ARIA labels for interactive elements
- Semantic HTML elements
- Proper form labels
- Focus states for interactive elements
